{"tid":635294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中港車違規左轉　再硬闖過路處　險橫掃途人","createTime":"2018-04-20T04:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T13:49:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bc923f5b88160b65a5bc6dc56789fce254a37f74","tid":635294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180420/photo/bkn-20180420113628097-0420_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180420115424\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180420%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180420113628097-0420_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180420115424&h=049552a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日有網民上載一段車Cam片，可見一輛掛有中港牌的私家車於路口違規左轉，更險撞向十數名正在過馬路的途人。片段一出，不少網民鬧爆司機「大地任我行」。<br />\n<br />\n從社交群組「香港交通突發報料區」的片段所見，於周三（18日）中午12時許，一輛掛有中港牌的私家車正沿荃灣沙咀道行駛，並於紅綠燈前等候燈號。<br />\n<br />\n當綠燈亮起後，私家車竟在「不准左轉」的指示牌前，左轉入大河道。更甚的是，當時有長者、推着嬰兒車的婦人等十數名途人正在過路，只見他們均被突然駛至的私家車嚇得目瞪口呆，急步走過馬路。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民大鬧該中港牌司機「危險」：「個牌都講明唔轉得左」、「只要有路，就算死路都任我行」。另有網民支持發貼者舉報司機，以免香港發生更多交通意外。<br />\n<br />\n根據運輸及房屋局近日回覆立法會財委會的文件指出，2017年有35,765名內地司機獲批免試簽發香港正式駕駛執照。而於2017年以免試簽發方式取得駕駛執照的駕駛者，則涉及469宗交通意外，較2015年的376宗上升逾兩成。"},{"pid":"8656795fba5bdc7ccb91e3c621dfabf73c84e57b","tid":635294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180420/bkn-20180420113628097-0420_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180420%2Fbkn-20180420113628097-0420_00822_001.html&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ab489838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180420/bkn-20180420113628097-0420_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"95d4f6558372bbcae8227301226eef89d94c95f4","tid":635294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd61bab6db424dc829cfcf6ca7ce204265090ce4","tid":635294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf7f56f23bab24c977fb7a8d866e0996d3e1d05","tid":635294,"uid":83097,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"起個司機底<br />\n殺左佢"},{"pid":"1fee4e8c948b0ddec7897955bd54726a224f4a30","tid":635294,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:21:08.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒"},{"pid":"1943270ff4ad5a197f6631f9973f4d16b3117d9f","tid":635294,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母今朝返工過馬路個陣都有個女人渣住架寶馬轉過黎<br />\n條路寫明不准右轉, 過馬路個邊仲要綠公仔緊<br />\n不過我上左行人路聽到人屌先見到佢仲要走埋<br />\n唔係真係企係佢前面塞住佢之後報警拉鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4c64185a4226d314d82ee738433b355cafb0ad","tid":635294,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:23:48.000Z","msg":"邊條柒頭 blur 左個車牌"},{"pid":"aad8b09b58afa7cd46c4aa2225f5df504e6fdcb8","tid":635294,"uid":176271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"保持通話"},{"pid":"0c1f688404e7ae70f797c3811ccac8215898f9d6","tid":635294,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:22:10.000Z","msg":"遮住個牌做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ac369c6f7bdf5fead15658bf0e188929bb3064","tid":635294,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:51:51.000Z","msg":"留名等睇警方唔係網上有片就查"},{"pid":"d3805d9d53eb520d467969da706b414b3d93ba06","tid":635294,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"香港二第公民<br />\n賤命來車死多D咪算<br />\n香港警察少D野做"},{"pid":"96e73bffd45b13d379e49ec9f